This article is a letter from former President Barack Obama to the Speaker of the House of Representatives and the President of the Senate. The letter discusses the continuation of the national emergency with respect to the proliferation of weapons of mass destruction. According to the National Emergencies Act, a national emergency automatically terminates unless the President publishes a notice stating that the emergency is to continue in effect. In accordance with this provision, Obama has sent a notice to the Federal Register stating that the national emergency declared in Executive Order 12938 will continue beyond November 14, 2016.